summary: A small spell that mimics the unrelenting force spell.
descriptionHtml:
[font=Verdana][size=3]The unrelenting force spell allows your character (of any level) to use the unrelenting force shout as a fire and forget spell.
[/size][/font][size=3]It is located at Jorrvaskr in Whiterun on the corner of the main table.
It does not use any scripts, nor require any other mods.
[/size]
author: Genocide400001
